 Toyota (Nigeria) Limited (TNL) has won the Automobile Brand of the Year Award at the Nigeria Business Leadership Awards organised by Business Day Newspaper. TNL came top in the Autobrand Category in the keenly contested category. TNL Managing Director, Mr. Kunle Ade-Ojo dedicated the award to the customers of Toyota, assuring them that the company will continue to offer the best in sales and aftersales. Ade-Ojo added that the company will continue to put in place structures that will add value to the company’s service delivery to ensure that the customers remain happy and committed to the brand. He announced that a budget vehicle will be launched in the first quarter of next year. “Expectedly, the vehicle is imbued with the superior quality and beauty of Toyota and worth looking forward to its introduction into the  market,” he said.